		<title>The money engines that built Fawry&#8217;s $1 billion business</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/04/20/how-fawry-built-a-profitable-fintech/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Emmanuel Nwosu]]></dc:creator>
