		<title>This Nigerian state is building 260 smart schools. Scale is the challenge.</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/04/17/enugu-smart-schools/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Frank Eleanya]]></dc:creator>
